name: CLEMENTINE
description:
My name is Clementine .... I was originally created using papers, inks, pencils and acrylic paint. This is a print of my original.

The original was professionally scanned at a high resolution and then printed professionally using archival inks on either photo paper (8x6 size) or low gloss heavy weight stock.

The watermark will of course not be on the print you receive.

I come in three sizes 
:: 8" x 6"
:: A4 size
:: A3 size

... and best of all I will arrive at your door in Australia with FREE postage.

If you live outside Australia then please contact me for accurate postage charge; as a guide it will be between $10 and $25 standard postage (insurance and tracking extra) for up to 5 prints posted internationally.
